## 🔧 Kritische regels (niet vergeten)

### 1. Namespace separator = dubbele punt
```
✅ data-i18n="create:form.name"
❌ data-i18n="create.form.name"
```

### 2. Laadvolgorde in `<head>` van ELKE pagina
```html
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/i18next@23/i18next.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/i18next-http-backend@2/i18nextHttpBackend.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/i18next-browser-languagedetector@7/i18nextBrowserLanguageDetector.min.js"></script>
<script src="/MyFamTreeCollab/js/i18n.js"></script>
```

### 3. Init patroon in `<body>` van ELKE pagina
```javascript
i18nModule.init().then(function() {
    i18nModule.loadNamespace('PAGINANAAM'); // ← aanpassen per pagina
    fetch('/MyFamTreeCollab/Layout/TopBar.html')
        .then(r => r.text())
        .then(html => i18nModule.onComponentLoaded(html, document.getElementById('topbar-placeholder')));
    // idem Navbar en Footer
});
```

### 4. Merknaam NIET vertalen
```html
<span>MyFamTreeCollab</span>  ✅
<span data-i18n="common:meta.appName"></span>  ❌
```

### 5. `onComponentLoaded()` regelt alles
Na fetch van TopBar/Navbar/Footer altijd via `i18nModule.onComponentLoaded()` — nooit direct `.innerHTML =`

